      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Saeed Bin Gazwan, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘You can give him from the <span class=\"iTxt\">Zakāt</span> until you enrich him’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "4. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from Sa‘id ibn Ghazwan who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Pay from Zakat until you make him rich (sufficient for his one year’s expenses).”’ "
        ]
      }
